text: Dolishniy Shepit (; ) is a commune (selsoviet) in Vyzhnytsia Raion, Chernivtsi Oblast, Ukraine. It is composed of four villages: Dolishniy Shepit, Falkiv (Фальків; Falcău), Lekechi (Лекечі; Lecheci) and Lopushna (Лопушна; Lăpușna). Category:Villages in Vyzhnytsia Raion
title: Dolishniy Shepit
